konqinfohelper
  Display information for some file types on Konqueror/Dolphin, mainly for usage
  when nepomuk is disabled.

Created by Phantom X
2010

Licensed under GPL. See COPYING file

--Requirements--
kdebase >= 4.4.0 (not tested in earlier, but can work)

--Optional--
aften (wave audio)
file (png image/avi container)
giflib/libungif (gif image)
id3lib (mp3 audio)
libmp4v2 (mp4 audio)
mkvtoolnix (matroska container)
mpgtx (mpeg video)
perl-image-exiftool or exiv2 (jpeg image)
poppler (pdf file)
torrentinfo (bittorrent file)
vorbis-tools (ogg audio)

--Instalation--

Run from this directory:

	make install

To uninstall execute:
	make uninstall
